{"tid":254632,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩迪：屌奶星！個西甲冠軍獎杯去左邊？？？？","createTime":"2017-05-23T10:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T22:35:29.000Z","uid":10338,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e37f6ce465e91e9e2b52bb2f57ad131d795817e","tid":254632,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:31:55.000Z","msg":"皇馬上一次奪得聯賽冠軍是在2012年，當時還要追溯到摩連奴執教期間，時隔五年再度奪冠，皇馬將士非常的興奮。不過客場作戰的皇馬，賽后並沒有被授予冠軍獎杯，同時也沒有頒獎儀式。當被告知西甲冠軍獎杯要在8月份，也就是下個賽季的第一個主場比賽被授予時，摩迪和巴爾都感到了不可思議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/23/183019_f6f23492861d04d98e0678124ed1a0c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F23%2F183019_f6f23492861d04d98e0678124ed1a0c3.jpg&h=57709ba2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/23/183019_e1bad2a414c434600fe0d0088aa71e75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F23%2F183019_e1bad2a414c434600fe0d0088aa71e75.jpg&h=b00572c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/23/183020_e1bad2a414c434600fe0d0088aa71e75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F23%2F183020_e1bad2a414c434600fe0d0088aa71e75.jpg&h=4d51f51a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f2b33505c9aad32ef71dd517c1b294cb8d882a0","tid":254632,"uid":1289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:36:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0858343850552b0dae0c2631d4778dbae192c12","tid":254632,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f629ec3b248a7ec7d8b9eebf13351504fb51d2b","tid":254632,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T10:39:00.000Z","msg":"ba